snippet.title: Best VGM 302 - Tales of Symphonia - Dry Trail
snippet.description:
Slow and High-Pitched version: https://youtu.be/5ZIAtIhGQzQ

See also:
Best VGM 152 - http://youtube.com/watch?v=fYvGx-PEAtg
Best VGM 185 - http://youtube.com/watch?v=m6HgGxxjyrU
Best VGM 1341 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VzHPc-HJlfM
Best VGM 1898 - https://youtu.be/Zys-MeBfBto
Best VGM 2003 - https://youtu.be/RAevlv9Y1ao

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gamecube
Tales of Symphonia
Dry Trail
